snippet.title: Tenebrae - Official Opening Cinematic
snippet.description:
Official Opening Cinematic for Tenebrae - Twilight of the Gods, a story-driven, fast-paced ARPG paying homage to early 90's classic such as Golden Axe, Rastan Saga and Metroidvania games while adding some fresh twists to the genre thanks to procedurally generated content.

http://www.tenebraegame.com
http://www.indiedb.com/games/tenebrae-twilight-of-the-gods
https://www.facebook.com/TenebraeGame/
